title: Saudi in, Vietnam out? A look at F1’s 2021 calendar
description: A look at the 2021 calendar and where will F1 go in place of Vietnam? Lando Norris starts an Esports team and a look ahead to the Turkish Grand Prix where Lewis Hamilton could match Michael Schumacher’s Championship record.
